NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Normally, Linda would bid 3H to show a heart control (void in this case). However, given partner bid hearts, the heart void is probably not useful. In fact, it is probably a detriment. That is why I think 3S is a better bid. 3H should show a heart card, not shortness once pard bids the suit. 4D by Yvon was fine and 4S now showed the spade Ace.|
