NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Control bids work as follows. When you bid the same suit twice, the first time you bid the suit it shows either first or second round control. If you repeat control bid the suit, it shows first round control. That rarely comes up with Italian control bids, but it does on occasion, as on this hand. Anyway, nice going.|
