^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Another very interesting hand. The dealer must be on drugs today, lol. Everything through my negative double is pretty standard. I am not quite strong enough to bid 2H, so I bid a negative double, I was then intending to bid 2H over 2D, to show long hearts and a hand not good enough for an immediate 2H bid. But, Linda screwed up my plans by bidding 5C, lol, which has merit by the law. There is a known 11 card fit. |
